channel.title: Strange problem
channel.description: ok so i really dont know what couldve caused this but when i try to log on itll say "your account is already loged in" and then [b]usually[/b] it will log me on but this time itll take a long time and just say error connecting to server even though my server was already up, baffled by this i took a look over at my server cmd prompt and it said [code] Starting TestScape Server on 0.0.0.0:43594 ClientHandler: Accepted from localhost:3858 Client type: high memory version UserId: 29861281 tom pwn3s y0 has signed onto server. Game saved for player _ ClientHandler: Client _ disconnected. ClientHandler: Accepted from localhost:3859 Client type: high memory version UserId: 29861281 tom pwn3s y0 has signed onto server. [/code] really strange huh? and i wasnt even loged in so i tried loging in again (just for the heck of it) a couple times and it kept saying i was still loged in and evry time i did it somthing like this would pop up on the server cmd prompt [code] ClientHandler: Accepted from localhost:3889 Client type: high memory version UserId: 29861281 tom pwn3s y0 has signed onto server. Game saved for player _ ClientHandler: Client _ disconnected. [/code] can any 1 figure this out? if i could have a guess i would say my client is deffective lol (shows what i know) still does any 1 have any ideas this is the first time i have seen this happen
